# Purpose and scope

- This repository is used to store and maintain subagents, skills, and prompts.
- Keep content modular, reusable, and easy to discover.
- Use snake-case for service/app names and folder/file names.
- Do not add README files that summarize completed work unless explicitly requested.
- Avoid nice-to-have functionality; deliver only what is required by the request.
